text: Enjoy privacy, river/beach access, and mountain views on five parcels totaling 86.57 tree-lined acres with income potential! This property includes a spacious home, barn, stables, garage/shop, and more! Large 1920's farmhouse home with hardwood floors and beautiful wood wrapped windows and doors features an unfinished basement and is mid-reno and ready for your imaginative touch. Huge garage/shop with loft area above featuring wood floors. Large barn with stables, additional paddocks, hay field, and a chicken coop with water and power. Fish the Skagit River from your property. So much potential - make it your own!

Charming single-story, 2-bedroom, 1 bath home. Spacious full bathroom with storage. Remodeled kitchen cabinets and granite countertops. Ample natural light from the South with newer vinyl windows. Partially fenced yard. Detached single-car garage and shop allows for plenty of storage at 550 sq/ft. Garage sold as-is. Plenty of off-street parking located on a quiet cul-de-sac street. Many options to put your personal touch in the home. Walking distance to nearby restaurants and The Store in Anacortes, at the top of Commercial Ave.

Desirable one level living in this charming 2 bedroom, 2 bath bungalow. Great in town location for easy access to local amenities. Spacious remodeled kitchen features quartz countertops, new cooktop/air fryer stove and newer fridge. Remodeled master bath with tiled shower and separate tub, quartz countertop with double sinks and heated floor. Private deck, patio and garden off of master bedroom. Custom front door. Beautifully landscaped yard with 2 decks for outdoor enjoyment. 1 car garage plus covered carport in addition to shop space, outdoor storage building and greenhouse. Newer siding is hand dipped cedar shakes. New electrical, plumbing & windows. Newer roof. This home has it all - just waiting for its new owners!

Centrally Located 4 bedroom rambler with a panoramic view of the mountains and valley. Just a short drive away are views of Mt Baker. Property includes a 3 stall hobby stable/shop and a large patio area in the backyard. Interiors include hardwood floors, large laundry and craft room, free standing gas stove in the family room. Lots of builtins and an open kitchen/dining area. Located in a very desireable setting with just a short drive to I-5. Also plenty of room to park your RV or boat!

Adorable single story, 2 bedroom, 1 bathroom home with a great layout, fresh exterior paint and a new roof! Fully fenced yard with lawn and room for a garden. Covered parking and large shed. Enjoy the mornings on the covered patio. Asphalt driveway and gated entry. Walking distance to downtown Burlington with fantastic dining and shopping and just moments to I5.

Welcome to this home. Great opportunity to bring fresh new decorating ideas. This home has 3 bedrooms and an extra large family room. Primary bedroom with bathroom. Living room with a fireplace. Country style kitchen. Dining room opens up to an oversized deck. Utility room on lower level. Fenced back yard. Home could benefit with some updates. 2 car garage. Located close to city forest lands, pool and local schools.

Spacious home with ample shop space, parking, & beautiful mountain & valley views in a peaceful setting. This property features a 1, 707 SF house, an oversized 840 SF 2-car garage, a 24 x 35 attached shop, & a 36 x 40 detached shop with 8' & 12' doors on a 0.86 acre lot. The home offers 3 bdrms & 1.75 baths, to include a primary suite with an en-suite bath. It also provides a practical kitchen, living & dining rooms, & a large laundry/utility room, ready for you to update everything just how you want it! Outside, there's plenty of space for a garden to complement the mature fruit trees, or enjoy the ample yard for playing & entertaining. A heat pump keeps you cool and comfortable all summer! Plenty of parking for your equipment, RV, or boat!

Nestled on 4.6 acres of pristine FLAT land. This scenic 2337 sqft modern farmhouse boasts a harmonious balance of rural bliss & modernity, minutes from downtown w/idyllic views of the sunset kissing the surrounding mountains. The barn/shop was designed to accommodate animals or your recreational toys. Explore your green thumb in the private blueberry garden, fruit orchard & chicken coop, while utilizing 4 fenced sections thoughtfully crafted for a hobby farm. Private backyard patio was designed to entertain w/a custom fire pit & covered BBQ area. Inside, discover a spacious laundry area, office, bath & primary bed w/a spa-like full bath on the main level. Upstairs, 3 bedrooms & a full bath provide ample space for guests. Not in Flood Zone

Stunning westerly views over Padilla Bay and over to Fidalgo Island from this just under 2 1/2 acre property. Now is your chance to own a piece of this wonderful area of Bayview in Skagit Valley. Available in street are water and electricity, buyer to verify with county for specifics. Survey map complete and property markers in. Come build your dream home and a shop plus maybe an ADU above, or a getaway abode, grow a garden or have a greenhouse and enjoy life just outside the city. Within minutes from some of the best local restaurants and places in Bow, Edison, La Conner and more. Don't miss this opportunity.

Situated on a large, level corner lot with great view of Mt Baker this fantastic, solidly built home has loads of character. This two bedroom 1 and 3/4 bath includes a large primary suite and attached bath. You'll enjoy the spacious loft and other bonus rooms needing only your imagination. Conveniently located just minutes from downtown, you'll love the vaulted ceilings and ample space this home provides. Plenty of parking with mature landscaping and, a metal roof this home is a must see!

Nestled in the heart of old town Mt Vernon, this vintage craftsman home exudes timeless charm & character. Step into enchanting details like coved ceilings, pristine white millwork, & wood-wrapped windows. Living area features a cozy gas FP w/ a decorative surround. A chef's delight, updated kitchen boasts SS apps, granite counters, white subway tile w/ farmhouse-style apron sink & A WIP! Oversized primary bedroom w/ double doors to back yard, WIC & luxurious updated ensuite bath featuring dual sink vanity & walk-in shower. 2 add'l bedrooms & full bath provide ample space for guests. Relax in the fenced backyard oasis featuring a sizable detached storage shed, alongside a convenient carport. Upgrades: on demand H2O heater, heat pump A/C.

Opportunity for an ample home with a garage, shop and RV parking in city limits! 3 bed/2.5 bath on its own fenced lot. Great floor plan with this bright open home with vaulted ceilings. Large master bedroom has walk-in closet and remodeled master bath with soaking tub and custom tiled shower. Both bathrooms have tiled flooring, new lighting and granite countertops. Ample kitchen with plenty of countertop space, solid oak cabinets, tile floor and skylights. Convenient desk space in the utility area and plenty of storage closets and extras throughout. Dont miss the RV parking, newer Hardi plank siding, AC and half bath out in the shop. Home comes with one year home warranty. NO HOA!

Discover comfort and convenience in this charming single-level 1-bed, 1-bath + office condo in Mount Vernon. Includes an attached 1-car garage, patio, and walk-in closet. Condo features new LVP floors throughout, ceiling fans, all new kitchen appliances + new washer/dryer, new gas furnace and garage opener. Perfect for modern living with updated amenities and a versatile office space large enough to be used as a spare bedroom. Located centrally for easy access to shops and parks. Ideal for down sizers seeking a low-maintenance lifestyle in a vibrant community 55 and older community with well maintained grounds and common space including community club house to host any events and socialize.

This beautiful stick built handcrafted home features three bedrooms, two full baths, and an attached two-car garage. Its open-concept design seamlessly integrates the dining room, living room, and kitchen featuring a stylish island and solid surface white quartz countertops. Abundant storage with a pantry, laminate flooring throughout. The primary suite offers a spacious walk-in closet and a generous bathroom. Ample windows provide abundant natural light and showcase views of the Cascade Mountains. Fully fenced backyard with a patio ready for great summer BBQs. Situated within walking distance of Silo Park and downtown Concrete. Additional features include a heat pump, and no HOA fees. Come, make this charming home yours today!

Beautiful 3 bed/1.75 bath LEVEL ENTRY home built by Landed Gentry in desirable Montreaux 55+ community. Over 1850/sf of living space with open great room design, plus separate formal sitting room. Kitchen features granite counters, stainless appliances, built-in pantry, pull-out shelving, large island w/seating, plus dining area. Great room with upgraded gas fireplace & hardwood floors. Primary suite has private bath w/double vanity, granite counter, walk-in shower & walk-in closet. Laundry w/utility sink. Covered patio plumbed for gas BBQ. Low maintenance yard. SunSetter automatic shades on key windows. Attached two car garage upgraded to add five additional feet of space, lots of storage.

This luxurious 3-bed, 2-bath home spans over 3, 200 sq ft and is flooded with natural light. The open-concept living area features a gourmet kitchen with ample counter space, cabinets, and pantry, while the main room includes a built-in office, perfect for remote work. The primary suite is a true retreat with a walk-in closet, a spa-like ensuite with a sauna, and a private balcony with serene water views. The lush outdoor space includes a 50-foot private dock, ideal for boating. The home is equipped with solar panels, ensuring energy efficiency. Additional features include hardwood floors, a cozy fireplace, ample storage, a 2-car attached garage, and a stair chair lift for easy access upstairs. This home perfectly blends luxury and comfort.

Private retreat with incredible views of Skagit Bay & the Olympic Mountains from almost every room. Quality renovations and upgrades throughout this impressive home. Vaulted ceilings, skylights & oversized windows make this home feel open & spacious. Beautiful hardwood, bamboo & cork floors highlight clean lines & artistic details throughout. Relax on the 500sq.ft deck or in the renovated sunroom off the master bedroom and enjoy the nightly sunset show. Discover the walk-in jetted soaking tub, whole home generator & surge protector, XL5 Thermador cooktop & more! The lower level offers a fully functioning ADU with private entrance and patio. Enjoy all of Shelter Bay's many amenities: pickleball, tennis, pool, playground, marina & more.

Turn key & adorable as can be, make this charmer yours! Located in Brickyard Creek w/3 bed, 1.75 bath, the current owners touch is evident w/tasteful updates throughout. Boasting an open concept floor plan w/vaulted ceilings, kitchen w/bar seating, cozy gas fireplace, dining area & grey oak laminate floors. Updates include new interior paint, bathroom mirrors, faucets, lighting fixtures in every part of the home, hardware, updated laundry room w/shelving, fencing & patio. Shy 1/4-acre lot makes for an expansive yard & includes a shed. RV parking, quiet cul-de-sac living yet close to town.

Alexa, find me the perfect home! Alright. I've found it. Welcome to this meticulously kept single level home w/solar panels, generator, & smart home system allowing voice control throughout! Natural light fills the main living area up to the vaulted ceilings. Put your couch around the gas fireplace w/the TV mounted above. Kitchen has rich-toned wood cabinets, granite countertops & stainless-steel appliances. Primary bedroom is privately located opposite from two additional bedrooms/bathroom & has a walk-in closet & full bathroom equipped with a double vanity shower & tub. Outside is the front porch of your dreams, along w/a large front yard & fenced backyard w/patio, gazebo, fire pit, garden space, & more! Shall I dial your agent now?

Looking for a place to get away? This very comfortable 480 sf cabin in the Cascade River Park. A gated for security, off grid community. This cabin was built in 2020 and also has a 160 sf covered porch, a large driveway for you and your friends with RV's to stay. A great open yard for lots of fun. The cabin has vaulted ceilings, sliding doors, nice appliances and fixtures, wood stove and propane heaters. The cabin is wired for a generator. There is lots of fire wood staked next to the porch. This is a great place to relax out side of the city. Lots of out door things to do. Fishing, hiking. exploring the Cascade forest. Come out and smell the fresh air, the smell of the forest and the campfire while you make good memories. Rentals are OK

3+ acres of beautifully established property. Private, yet convenient access to I5. Huge shop w/ loft storage, boat/RV parking, workshop area w/ wood stove. Green house, and large garden space. Charming farmhouse w/ durable metal roof. 3 bedrooms w/ dormers and 2 baths upstairs. All blinds throughout home are new. Main floor has large living and dining rooms that lead into bright kitchen w/plentiful cabinet & counter space. Dining area has french doors opening to the backyard. This property has a LOT to offer, come and check it out. You wont want to miss out on this one.

Perched in the highly sought after San Juan Passage, this Nantucket-style abode boasts breathtaking vistas of Guemes Channel and the bustling ferry traffic. Offering direct access to the beach, a coveted amenity for waterfront living, it also features a pickleball court and a charming amphitheater park, perfect for outdoor gatherings. The main floor boasts a serene primary bedroom, offering convenience and comfort. Step onto the balcony to soak in the panoramic views, or retreat to the lovely backyard with its spacious patio, ideal for summer dining or simply basking in the tranquility of the coastal ambiance. This home seamlessly blends coastal charm with modern comforts, providing an idyllic retreat in a picturesque setting.

Step into serene living at Sedro Woolley's Premier 55+ Community! Nestled in a picturesque space, you'll be hard-pressed to find anything like it again. A modern residence, complete w/a cook's kitchen ideal for dining and casual meals at the peninsula; a generous and relaxing primary featuring an ensuite bathroom with a spacious shower, linen closet, and ample storage. Natural light abounds from numerous windows while offering views of lush green landscapes. Enjoy A/C and ceiling fans to enhance airflow and energy efficiency, providing comfort year-round. The Powered Oversized Shed makes the perfect space for hobbies & additional storage needs. Don't miss this rare opportunity to downsize to an affordable community in a tranquil environment

Take a look at this charming home, located just minutes from the heart of Mount Vernon with Mount Baker views. This 3 bed 2 bath home, features an open floor plan, with a bright and open kitchen, full bath off the Primary bedroom, and newly covered front deck. The spacious, oversized, 2 car garage offers plenty of space for vehicles and storage, as well as a new door and power lift with video/audio capabilities. Affordable home in a great neighborhood, close to schools, shopping, parks and trails.

Water and Septic is on site. This lot in the Skagitwilde Community is ready for you. Bring your build plans or new manufactured home. The 3 bedroom Septic was placed in 2009. Trails here will take you to Finney Creek and the Skagit River. Year-round opportunities are endless. The Fly Fishing on the Skagit is amazing! Come enjoy everything that this community has to offer!!

Nestled on 11+ acres in Skagit Valley, this Henry Klein-designed home (and former personal residence) features his signature wood accents & expansive windows. Enjoy the open dining with wooden beams and a cozy wood stove in the high-ceilinged living room. The primary bedroom offers ample closets & new floors. Ascend the unique spiral staircase to a lofted office and storage space. The 1965 addition adds two bedrooms & a family room, perfect for multigenerational living. Outside, discover 3 acres of open land plus 8 acres of forest trails & a beaver pond. Multiple decks, large carport, 2 RV hookups, a play area, & animal pens complete this versatile estate, ready for your vision to unfold. This is a dream property with endless possibilities.

Discover the perfect canvas for your custom home in a prime location close to downtown. This level residential lot offers good potential views of the city and Padilla Bay. Easy access to shopping or Highway 20. All city utilities are readily available simplifying the building process! The absence of CCR's provides the freedom to design and construct your ideal living space without restriction. Don't miss your chance to be part of this well established neighborhood and the wonderful community of Anacortes!

Embrace the allure of waterfront living on Fidalgo Island with southern exposure views of the bay and Whidbey Island. This beach cabin presents a unique opportunity to craft your ideal retreat with 122 feet of medium bank waterfront. Revel in the convenience of one-level living within this 1104 SF, 2 BD, 1.75 BA home, complemented by a detached garage and charming backyard retreat. Whether you're seeking a weekend escape or a year-round sanctuary, this property offers unrivaled potential. Just a scenic 90-minute drive from Seattle and Vancouver, immerse yourself in the serenity of this idyllic waterfront setting, conveniently close to Deception Pass bridge and NAS Whidbey. Don't miss your chance to make this dream a reality!

Price improvement on this adorable mid-century charmer in the heart of Anacortes. Walkable to 3 schools, restaurants, medical and stores, this charmer is situated on a corner lot with views of Mt. Baker and peekaboos of Fidalgo Bay. Spacious living room with built-ins, cozy gas fireplace with newer LVP floors. Dining room with wood parquet floors. Kitchen with new butcher block counters and original design features. Bathroom offers walk-in shower and is equipped with stackable washer/dryer. Great storage space in the basement - perfect for a home gym! Cute terraced yard with space for a garden. Newer windows and roof. Detached garage off the alley has potential to convert to an ADU. So many possibilities. Don't miss this one!

Turn-key rambler nestled on a sunny lot in the desirable Copper Pond neighborhood! This charming 3-bed home offers single-level living on a quiet dead-end street. Enjoy vaulted ceilings & a sprawling layout w/large centralized kitchen that opens to all living spaces. The kitchen boasts breakfast bar seating, while the dining, great room & formal living room provide ample space for gatherings. Retreat to the primary bedroom featuring an en-suite bath & large walk-in closet. Recessed lighting, private backyard w/mature landscaping, fruit trees, garden space, & a spacious deck make this home one-of-a-kind. Newer furnace, home security system, automatic sprinkler system, whole house wired generator, 2 car garage & all appliances included!

Northwest Chalet style home. Well maintained with updated kitchen, solid surface counters, quality cabinets & stainless steel appliances. Engineered hardwood flooring in living area, cozy wood burning stove & big windows. Large wrap around deck on main level and fenced back yard for outdoor entertaining. Nice sized Laundry/utility room off kitchen. One bedroom one bath on each level, Primary bedroom has built in storage, office/ hobby area, and a deck to enjoy. Detached Studio to use as work out area, office, guest room. Oversized detached garage, with custom cabinetry. Level yard. Community amenities include, swimming pool, tennis & Pickle courts, golf, private beaches, BBQ & picnic areas, Library, club house, marina, boat launch ramp.

Discover your dream mini farm! Nestled on a fully fenced acre, this charming 3-bedroom, 1-bath farmhouse offers comfort, versatility, and beauty. Upon entering, you are welcomed by a spacious living and dining area, an updated kitchen, and a main bedroom and bathroom. Upstairs, you'll find 2 bedrooms, while the basement awaits your creative touch. Outdoor amenities include a greenhouse, storage/potting shed, chicken coop, and a beautiful 2-stall barn with gorgeous views of the San Juans and stunning sunsets. The garden area boasts fig, peach, pear, nut, and apple trees. 2 RV hookups, one on a cement pad w/septic/power/water - permitted and ready to build a DADU. Enjoy the serenity of this special property with room to grow!

Charming and well-maintained rambler on 1.28 level acres in desirable Bayview! This 3 bed/1.75 bath rambler not only boasts an attached 2 car garage but also a 36 x 36 shop w/ a workshop area & another 20 x 24 shop! Mature low-maintenance landscaping & the privacy of country living surrounds you. Front door opens to vaulted ceilings, great natural lighting, a cozy gas fireplace w/ marble surround, & picturesque views of the property from the open-concept living room + dining room. Kitchen features beautiful wood cabinets, durable luxury vinyl flooring, and east facing bay windows w/ breakfast nook. Sizable primary bedroom features: bay windows, a walk-in closet, & an attached full bathroom with granite. Two additional bedrooms & 3/4 bath.

Welcome to this charming starter home / Investment property located on the West side! This delightful home boasts a new roof and ductless heating system, 3 bedrooms and 1 recently remolded bathroom, original hardwood floors, single car garage with storage above. this cozy abode is perfect for first-time buyers or savvy investors looking to add to their portfolio. The fenced back yard provides space for outdoor entertaining. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this gem your own!

Incredible opportunity to acquire a well-maintained 5-plex in beautiful Anacortes in great condition! With all five units currently leased, this property guarantees immediate rental income and a hassle-free investment. 3 units are 2 bed/ 1 bath. 2 units are 1 bed/ 1 bath. Washers and dryers in each unit. Each unit has its own electrical meter that renter pays. Seller pays for Water/Sewer/Garbage. Boasting a cap rate of 5.98%, this 5-plex is a valuable addition to any portfolio. Whether you're an experienced investor looking to expand or a newcomer seeking a solid market entry, this property offers both stability and growth potential. Dont miss out on owning a high-performing asset in one of Washingtons most desirable locations!

This house has everything you are looking for!! Updated throughout 1 year ago with all new interior and exterior paint. Kitchen has quartz counters, tile backsplash and stainless steel appliances and large island. 4 bedrooms and 2 full baths with 2 bonus rooms that could be bedrooms, offices, dens or playrooms. All the rooms in the house are large including walk in closets. True formal dining area with bonus butlers pantry/coffee bar. Large corner fenced lot with gazebo that stays with sale, oversized two car garage with additional heated separate storage room/ workspace and poured concrete walkways and driveway. This home is located within walking distance to schools, shopping and dining. Don't miss out on this one!

Open floor plan corner lot rambler with abundant windows, rich vinyl plank flooring, shop, fruit trees, and garden space along a gorgeous greenbelt near the Skagit River. The living room features vaulted ceiling and charming corner stove. Light and bright kitchen with oversized eating counter and plenty of storage. Primary bedroom includes attached bath with storage. Gorgeous outdoor space with partially fenced yard and oversized, partially covered patio plus garden beds, fire pit, and RV parking. Shop features roll up door, and a man door, plus covered outdoor storage for both firewood and toys. Home features a low maintenance metal roof, forced air heating and cooling, and is wired for a generator!

Discover this newly renovated mid-century rambler blending contemporary & industrial flair. Nestled in the Skagit Golf & Country Club, this home features vaulted ceilings, open layout & striking wood beams. Accented clear story windows flood the living space w/natural light. Kitchen boasts new appliances & soft-close cabinets. California bi-fold doors create the perfect indoor-outdoor living space. Primary suite offers skylit bath & french doors to new deck w/swim spa. Combined living & dining rm w/floor-to-ceiling windows, private front patio w/lush landscaping. Spacious laundry rm w/wine fridge, 2nd bedrm w/barn door closet, insulated shop w/heat/AC, 2-car garage, & ample driveway parking for RVs/boats & multiple cars.Truly one-of-a-kind!

Immerse yourself in tranquility; boasting breathless, panoramic views! With the majestic Cascade mountains/farmland as your backdrop, minutes to Skagit Valley Golf CC, this property offers the perfect blend of luxury living with functionality. Vaulted ceilings, open floorplan, expanded hardwoods, covered privacy patio, fenced backyard, lovely porch, gas FP. Upper L: primary suite offers views, spaciousness, dual sinks, 2 linen & huge W/I closet, laundry. Granite countertops, island, SS appl. Lower L: bed/bath, huge rec room & dream 4-car garage!!! More than a house; it's a lifestyle! Whether you're seeking a permanent residence or a peaceful retreat, this property promises an unforgettable living experience. 12-mo home buyer warranty

This beautiful farmhouse style features 3 bed 2 bath with 1, 574 sqft of living space, 2 car garage that has 12' tall ceilings, and a covered front porch. This home plan offers many upgrades such as an open concept great room with luxury vinyl plank flooring, upgraded cabinets with soft close, quartz countertops, tile backsplash, vaulted ceilings, walk in pantry, primary bedroom walk in closet, mini splits for heating and cooling, and exterior hot water. Don't miss this opportunity to own a newer constructed home close to downtown and all downtown amenities. Schedule your showing time today!

Welcome to this beautiful craftsman charmer in the heart of the Sedro Woolley. This well kept bungalow boasts new paint inside and out, new roof, new hot water heater, newer furnace & new vinyl windows. Kitchen comes complete with all appliances, tons of cabinet space and a breakfast nook. Home features 3 bedrooms, bonus room, spacious living room, dining room and basement. Basement is 95% completed with 1 bedroom, bonus room and full bath. This corner lot offers you a huge fenced-in yard, detached garage and RV parking! The lovely covered front porch, mature landscaping and patios in both the front and back yard, make this the perfect oasis for relaxation after a long day! Walking distance to schools, restaurants and shops! Welcome Home!

Discover the inviting warmth of this energy-efficient, better than new home boasting functional spaces and upgrades throughout. The spacious kitchen is a chef's dream, complete with a walk-in pantry and plenty of natural light. Enjoy the calming & serene environment as you take in mountain views from the spacious primary suite with spa-like ensuite bath. The den/office on the main floor features a window seat & potential 5th bedroom. Outside you'll find a fully fenced backyard oasis with added flagstone patios, perfect for relaxing & entertaining. The low-maintenance yard includes a storage shed, while the attached 3 car garage provides added parking and storage convenience. Montreaux is a premier neighborhood, don't miss this opportunity!

Adorable home in the heart of Burlington. Have you imagined walking to town for meals, parks, or shopping? This 3 bed 2.5bath home has main level living with primary on main. Main level also has bright kitchen with large island, half bath, office, and dining area with slider out to yard. Upper level with 2 bedrooms and full bath. Backyard with covered deck, fully fenced, and outbuildings for your hobbies. 2 car garage with extra parking on side plus gate to park RV/boat behind with electric hookup or 220v for EV charging. Close distance to I5 for commuting. 8X16 shed with porch and loft is spray foamed, wired and drywalled and can be additionally negotiated.

A beautiful well appointed home with covered wrap around porch, a large back deck w/ fenced back yard, Huge front yard! Abuts ACFL Little Cranberry Lake Park and trails. Very comfortable, 4 bedrooms, wood or stone flooring. Floorplan flows very nicely. Super home for entertaining. Large kitchen with eating bar and gorgeous real wood cabinets with loads of storage space. Home exterior repainted in 2023, well maintained and loved. Seller owns vacant land also behind this parcel. Willing to split off a portion for a cost, to expand your space. 1344 sq ft garage/shop. Has own heater. House has connected generator for power outage comfort/safety. Views of Mt. Baker and Guemes Channel. Neighborhood close to town. Great listing!
